ious when it began using bones."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets."},{"version":"diamond","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"pearl","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"platinum","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It has been seen pounding boulders with the bone it carries in order to tap out messages to others."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It collects bones from an unknown place. Some whisper that a MAROWAK graveyard exists somewhere in the world."},{"version":"black","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"white","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"black-2","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"white-2","text":"From its birth, this savage Pok\u00e9mon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons."},{"version":"x","text":"It is small and was originally very weak. Its temperament turned ferocious when it began using bones."},{"version":"y","text":"The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken."},{"version":"sun","text":"Originally, it was weak and timid. After evolution, its temperament becomes violent, and it begins to wield bones as weapons."},{"version":"moon","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon is out for vengeance on its natural enemy, Mandibuzz. It throws bones like boomerangs to try to take it down."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It throws bones at Mandibuzz to knock it down. It\u2019s thought that Marowak is trying to avenge its parent."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"They thump their bones rhythmically to communicate among themselves. There are nearly 50 different rhythmic patterns."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Small and weak, this Pok\u00e9mon is adept with its bone club. It has grown more vicious over the ages."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Small and weak, this Pok\u00e9mon is adept with its bone club. It has grown more vicious over the ages."},{"version":"sword","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon overcame its sorrow to evolve a sturdy new body. Marowak faces its opponents bravely, using a bone as a weapon."},{"version":"shield","text":"When this Pok\u00e9mon evolved, the skull of its mother fused to it. Marowak\u2019s temperament also turned vicious at the same time."}],"evo":{"name":"cubone","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"marowak","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/105.png","shiny"